title: Tenorshare Data Recovery Professional 4.4.0
description:
Tenorshare Data Recovery Professional 4.4.0 Build 2014.7.8 | 5 Mb

Tenorshare Data Recovery Professional is a powerful data recovery program. It not only support recovering data with Windows file system (FAT12, FAT16, FAT32, NTFS), but also Mac file system (HFS, HFS+) and Linux file system (EXT2, EXT3). Lost data due to virus attack PC, corrupted partition, drive crash, system sabotage, etc. can be retrieved easily with it
